  "title": "IT Service Desk Analyst / Assistant Engineer (24×7 Operations)",
  "description": "<p><em>(2-Year Contract | Renewable & Convertible)</em></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Bukit Gombak <br /><strong>Allowances:</strong> With Site and Shift Allowances<br /><strong>Work Hours:</strong> 12-hour rotating shifts (Day/Night), 3–4 days per week<br /><strong>Environment:</strong> Secure site (No-camera zone; lockers provided)</p><p>Our client is seeking <strong>Service Desk Analysts/Assistant Engineer </strong>to support a <strong>24/7 Service Desk</strong>, ensuring high availability of enterprise IT services and timely restoration of services in a mission-critical environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p><ul><li>Monitor enterprise IT networks and server systems</li><li>Act as the single point of contact for users, resolver teams, and vendors</li><li>Respond to hotline calls and emails within agreed SLAs</li><li>Take ownership of incidents and service requests through to resolution</li><li>Track, update, and close tickets within defined timelines</li><li>Maintain accurate documentation and incident records</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p><ul><li>Minimum Higher NITEC in IT or related discipline</li><li>1–2 years of relevant experience</li><li>Strong customer service, communication, and teamwork skills</li><li>Experience in a NOC / Service Desk environment is preferred</li><li>Comfortable working 12-hour rotating shifts, including weekends and public holidays</li><li>Able to work in a secure, no-camera environment</li></ul></p><p><strong>To Apply</strong></p><p>To apply or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to:<br /><a href=\"https://www.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/job/general-management/assistant-export-control-manager-star-career-consulting-b2246758d92b888acc7acec3fd2c4c67#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn.tay@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><strong>Lynn Tay</strong> (Reg. No. R1876711)<br /><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD</strong> (EA Licence: 20C0353)</p>",
